QuestData.Title: Quit Vining!
QuestData.Description:
This is terrible, $n! We got harvesters that ain't harvestin'!
We've been busting our rumps chopping down all these trees, but someone keeps tangling up our machines in the vines! I ain't going out there with those night elves stalkin' around.
See if you can get in there and free up my equipment!
